ralian_Government\"}, {\"begin\": 354, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9976027419688417, \"rank\": 0.0021810736946128472, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Deputy Chair of the Committee,Mrs Melissa McIntosh MP, said: 'The Committee looks forward to speaking with the Australian Olympic Committee to learn more about its engagement with public health campaigns and the 2032 Brisbane Olympic Games.'\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 491, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_McIntosh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Melissa McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_McIntosh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_McIntosh\"}, {\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Date: Wednesday, 20 March 2024  Time: 9.15am - 10.00am AEDT (Canberra time)  Location: Committee Room 1R6, Parliament House, Canberra  A program for the public hearing is available on theinquiry website.\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999805836526, \"rank\": 1.9416323623864545e-08, \"text\": \"AEDT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parlia